useReducer use to manage multiple states or multiple state hook
it takes 2 arguments (reducerFunction,initial state/current value)
syntax for useReducer hook const  [state,dispatch] =useReducer(reducerFunction,initial state/current value) 
dispatch : to trigger action method
reducer function :it is a pure functions(a function which does not produce any side effects) that take in(accepts) a  state and action and returns a new state.
given the set of inputs it should returns the same output always.
we need to define reducer function can be in same component before main function or can be in diff components.it takes 2 args (state,action) and it need to return something
